title: BBC - BBC Wildlife Magazine [2010-2012, PDF, ENG]
description:
BBC Wildlife Magazine is a celebration of the natural world, featuring all the latest discoveries, news and views on wildlife, conservation and environmental issues. With strong broadcasting links, authoritative journalism and award-winning photography, BBC Wildlife Magazine is essential reading for anyone with a passion for wildlife who wants to understand, experience and enjoy nature more. magazine about wildlife in English. Very colorful and has a lot of illustrations of authentic and interesting articles about animals. It may be useful to animal lovers and people interested in living in English.
